channel.title: Serverstatus page
channel.description:
"This server has already been posted, but not yet approved, have some patience!."
I've waited for over 20+ hours yet the server hasn't appeared on the page.
I've done everything correctly, logged in with the user and pass specified. I opened the link on the vps. Yet nothing.
I'd appreciate the assistance, thanks in advance.

item.title: Serverstatus page
item.dc:creator: @moparisthebest Moparisthebest
item.description:
@moparisthebest wrote:

Snow_:

I think there might be a problem with the status page. There haven’t been any new admissions since 10/03, the day MITB upgraded his server.

Good catch, no cronjobs have been running at all since then due to a PAM bug that was super hard to track down, it should be fixed now. Thanks!
